<li>Gitton, Bernard. "Time, like an everflowing stream." Trans. Mlle. Annie Chadeyron. Ed. Anthony Randall. Horological Journal 131.12 (June 1989): 18-20.</li>
<li>Taylor, Robert. "<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.sinorama.com.tw/en/print_issue.php3?id=199668506116E.TXT&mag=past">Taiwan's Biggest Cuckoo Clock?: Recreating an Astronomical Timepiece</a>". Sinorama Magazine. 3-15-2006</li>
<li>Xuan, Gao. "Principle Research and Reconstruction Experiment of the Astronomical Clock Tower in Ancient China." Proceeding of the 11th World Congress in Mechanism and machine Science. August 18–21, 2003. Tianjin, China.</li>
</ul>
